Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:49.48,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想参加决赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:50.49,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢? 优希
