Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就躲在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了!
